{"hash":"40d5a017cb271761700a8ea3fe775477dafeabda","data":{"post":{"title":"Detect network online/offline State using JavaScript","date":"June 20, 2020","content":"<h2 id=\"detect-current-online-state\"><a href=\"#detect-current-online-state\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Detect Current online state</h2>\n<p>We can detect if the user is <code>online</code> or <code>offline</code> by using the <code>onLine</code> property on the <code>navigator</code> object which will return <code>true</code> if the user is connected to the internet, otherwise it returns <code>false</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">navigator</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">onLine</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #676E95\">//true if has internet otherwise false</span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"detect-internet-connection-state-change\"><a href=\"#detect-internet-connection-state-change\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Detect internet connection state change</h2>\n<p><code>online</code> and <code>offline</code> events will be triggered if the user's internet connections state changes. So we can add an <code>online</code> and <code>offline</code> event listener to the <code>window</code> and perform respective actions based on the online and offline state.</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki\" style=\"background-color: #292D3E\"><code><span style=\"color: #C792EA\">function</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">updateStatus</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">(){</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">if</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(navigator</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">onLine)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">{</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">console</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">log</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">Your connected</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">}</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">else</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">{</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">console</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">log</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">Connection lost</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">}</span>\n<span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">}</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">window</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">addEventListener</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">online</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">updateStatus</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span>\n<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">window</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #82AAFF\">addEventListener</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">offline</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">,</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #A6ACCD\">updateStatus</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">)</span><span style=\"color: #89DDFF\">;</span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<p>Please donate <a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/jagathishSaravanan?locale.x=en_GB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>, for making more tutorials.</p>\n","tags":[{"title":"JavaScript","path":"/tag/JavaScript/"},{"title":"jstip","path":"/tag/jstip/"}]}},"context":{}}